    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Our Portfolio</strong> is a <strong><u>Story-based simulation game</u></strong> that tells the story of Seohyun, who is struggling to find a job after graduating from university. To build her portfolio, she joins an indie game development team with the help of Minha, her high school friend. The game covers a year of Seohyun's journey in the team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Please help Seohyun, who is new to game development, successfully complete the game!!</strong></u> </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > <strong>Character Introduction</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras/17f7245c5adf0da6da62b42bba9d3fe6.avif?t=1736313148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras_big/17f7245c5adf0da6da62b42bba9d3fe6.avif?t=1736313148 width=800 height=580 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras/998a211b451b7a4504ee80328e5b56f6.avif?t=1736313148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras_big/998a211b451b7a4504ee80328e5b56f6.avif?t=1736313148 width=800 height=580 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras/6a6a90384b6ef029ce4cc173e1cb7e81.avif?t=1736313148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras_big/6a6a90384b6ef029ce4cc173e1cb7e81.avif?t=1736313148 width=800 height=580 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras/c5768c45646b457ccc266ab9b2728f95.avif?t=1736313148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras_big/c5768c45646b457ccc266ab9b2728f95.avif?t=1736313148 width=800 height=580 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras/3a6f534f5bb958d696b4995c2ebdd28d.avif?t=1736313148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras_big/3a6f534f5bb958d696b4995c2ebdd28d.avif?t=1736313148 width=800 height=580 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras/74790ef865cb2cde232d773e13dcb718.avif?t=1736313148\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222570/extras_big/74790ef865cb2cde232d773e13dcb718.avif?t=1736313148 width=800 height=580 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Diverse story content and a setting that highlights the unique characteristics of Daegu</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > By building rapport, you can unlock a total of 24 behind-the-scenes stories, experiencing the unique charms of the characters. The game also enhances immersion with background illustrations of real locations and over 20 CG illustrations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The protagonist who grows through development activities</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > With simple controls, you can develop the character while feeling as though you're growing together with the protagonist. Through three types of mini-games and more than 20 choices, you manage buffs and debuffs, helping the character develop and ultimately succeed in landing a job.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
